description:
Jazz Bassist Ron Carter discusses his part on one of the most influential Hip Hop records of all time. A Tribe Called Quest: Low End Theory. This is an excerpt from the full interview back in 2012. Please check it out! 

Thanks for watching and please subscribe to us and give a like button. Subscribing really helps us out because you are notified when new videos come out. Share this video on social media if you enjoy it because it helps keep jazz alive. Thank you! 

See the full video interview at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w3Rw1s6L-OA
